        <obo:IAO_0000115>Adult descending neuron of the posterior brain of the DNpe052 group (Berg et al., 2025). It belongs to the SMPpv2 ventral hemilineage (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral lateral accessory lobe, accessory mesothoracic neuropil, lateral horn, epaulette, vest, posterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, anterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, superior clamp, inferior clamp, wedge, flange and T1 leg neuropil, and the gnathal ganglion, saddle and abdominal neuromere (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral lateral accessory lobe, accessory mesothoracic neuropil, epaulette, vest, posterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, anterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, superior clamp, inferior clamp, flange, T1 leg neuropil and T3 leg neuropil, and the gnathal ganglion, saddle and abdominal neuromere (Berg et al., 2025). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <terms:contributor rdf:resource="http://orcid.org/0000-0002-1373-1705"/>
        <terms:date rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2020-07-30T12:00:00Z</terms:date>
        <oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>fly_anatomy.ontology</oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>
        <oboInOwl:hasRelatedSynonym>AVLP564</oboInOwl:hasRelatedSynonym>
        <oboInOwl:hasRelatedSynonym>DNxl076</oboInOwl:hasRelatedSynonym>
        <oboInOwl:id>FBbt:20000673</oboInOwl:id>
        <rdfs:comment>Cell type identified in multiple EM datasets (Scheffer et al., 2020; Schlegel et al., 2024; Dorkenwald et al., 2024; Marin et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025). Synapse locations are given where each cell of this type in neuprint has at least 10 connections. Hemilineage information from neuprint, though original source not clear.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>adult descending neuron of the posterior brain DNpe052</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
    <owl:Axiom>
        <owl:annotatedSource rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_20000673"/>
        <owl:annotatedProperty rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115"/>
        <owl:annotatedTarget>Adult descending neuron of the posterior brain of the DNpe052 group (Berg et al., 2025). It belongs to the SMPpv2 ventral hemilineage (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral lateral accessory lobe, accessory mesothoracic neuropil, lateral horn, epaulette, vest, posterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, anterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, superior clamp, inferior clamp, wedge, flange and T1 leg neuropil, and the gnathal ganglion, saddle and abdominal neuromere (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral lateral accessory lobe, accessory mesothoracic neuropil, epaulette, vest, posterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, anterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, superior clamp, inferior clamp, flange, T1 leg neuropil and T3 leg neuropil, and the gnathal ganglion, saddle and abdominal neuromere (Berg et al., 2025). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025).</owl:annotatedTarget>
