        <owl:annotatedSource rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_20001025"/>
        <owl:annotatedProperty rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115"/>
        <owl:annotatedTarget>Adult descending neuron of the posterior brain of the DNpe040 group (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral gorget, epaulette, vest, posterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, anterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, posterior lateral protocerebrum, inferior clamp and superior posterior slope, and the gnathal ganglion, inferior bridge, saddle, lower tectulum, intermediate tectulum and abdominal neuromere (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral gorget, epaulette, posterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, anterior ventrolateral protocerebrum and inferior clamp, the contralateral antennal mechanosensory and motor center, vest and flange, and the gnathal ganglion, inferior bridge, lower tectulum, intermediate tectulum and abdominal neuromere (Berg et al., 2025). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025).</owl:annotatedTarget>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>FlyBase:FBrf0246888</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>FlyBase:FBrf0259490</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
