        <oboInOwl:hasRelatedSynonym>DNxn137</oboInOwl:hasRelatedSynonym>
        <oboInOwl:id>FBbt:20001039</oboInOwl:id>
        <rdfs:comment>Cell type identified in multiple EM datasets (Scheffer et al., 2020; Schlegel et al., 2024; Dorkenwald et al., 2024; Marin et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025). Synapse locations are given where each cell of this type in neuprint has at least 10 connections. Hemilineage information from neuprint, though original source not clear.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>adult descending neuron of the posterior brain DNp101</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
