        <obo:IAO_0000115>Adult descending neuron of the posterior brain of the DNpe037 group (Berg et al., 2025). It belongs to the DM6 central2 hemilineage (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral gorget, epaulette, vest, posterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, posterior lateral protocerebrum, inferior clamp, superior posterior slope and cantle, and the saddle and intermediate tectulum (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral gorget, vest, posterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, posterior lateral protocerebrum, inferior clamp, superior posterior slope, cantle and wing neuropil, the contralateral superior posterior slope, cantle and wing neuropil, and the gnathal ganglion, saddle and intermediate tectulum (Berg et al., 2025). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <terms:contributor rdf:resource="http://orcid.org/0000-0002-1373-1705"/>
        <terms:date rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2020-07-30T12:00:00Z</terms:date>
