        <obo:IAO_0000115>Adult descending neuron of the posterior brain of the DNpe028 group (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral posterior lateral protocerebrum, inferior clamp, antler and superior posterior slope, and the gnathal ganglion, inferior bridge, lower tectulum and intermediate tectulum (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral antennal mechanosensory and motor center and T3 leg neuropil, and the gnathal ganglion, lower tectulum, intermediate tectulum and abdominal neuromere (Berg et al., 2025). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <terms:contributor rdf:resource="http://orcid.org/0000-0002-1373-1705"/>
        <terms:date rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2020-07-30T12:00:00Z</terms:date>
