        <obo:IAO_0000115>Adult descending neuron of the posterior brain of the DNpe001 group (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral superior medial protocerebrum, gorget, vest, antler and superior posterior slope, the contralateral antler, and the inferior bridge and lower tectulum (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral lateral accessory lobe, vest and T1 leg neuropil, and the gnathal ganglion, inferior bridge, lower tectulum and intermediate tectulum (Berg et al., 2025). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <terms:contributor rdf:resource="http://orcid.org/0000-0002-1373-1705"/>
