        <obo:IAO_0000115>Adult descending neuron of the outside anterior cluster of the DNde003 group (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral lateral accessory lobe, vest, wedge, superior posterior slope, inferior posterior slope and T1 leg neuropil, and the ventral nerve cord and gnathal ganglion (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral lateral accessory lobe, vest, inferior posterior slope and T1 leg neuropil, and the ventral nerve cord and gnathal ganglion (Berg et al., 2025). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025).</obo:IAO_0000115>
