        <obo:IAO_0000115>Adult descending neuron of the posterior brain of the DNpe023 group (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral lateral accessory lobe, vest, wedge, superior posterior slope and inferior posterior slope, the contralateral lateral accessory lobe, gorget and vest, and the gnathal ganglion, saddle and intermediate tectulum (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral lateral accessory lobe and vest, the contralateral lateral accessory lobe, gorget, vest and inferior posterior slope, and the gnathal ganglion and intermediate tectulum (Berg et al., 2025). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <terms:contributor rdf:resource="http://orcid.org/0000-0002-1373-1705"/>
