        <obo:IAO_0000115>Adult lobula visual projection neuron of the LoVP17 group (Berg et al., 2025). It belongs to the VPNp&amp;v1 posterior hemilineage (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral lobula layer 6, posterior lateral protocerebrum and superior clamp (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral posterior lateral protocerebrum, superior clamp and inferior clamp (Berg et al., 2025). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <terms:contributor rdf:resource="http://orcid.org/0000-0002-1373-1705"/>
        <terms:date rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2020-07-30T12:00:00Z</terms:date>
