        <obo:IAO_0000115>Adult descending neuron of the anterior ventral brain of the DNbe005 group (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral antennal mechanosensory and motor center, vest, posterior lateral protocerebrum, wedge, superior posterior slope, inferior posterior slope, cantle and wing neuropil, the contralateral wedge, superior posterior slope, inferior posterior slope and wing neuropil, and the cervical connective, gnathal ganglion, inferior bridge, lower tectulum, intermediate tectulum and abdominal neuromere (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral wing neuropil, T1 leg neuropil and neck neuropil, the contralateral antennal mechanosensory and motor center, wing neuropil, T1 leg neuropil and neck neuropil, and the gnathal ganglion, lower tectulum, intermediate tectulum and abdominal neuromere (Berg et al., 2025).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <terms:contributor rdf:resource="http://orcid.org/0000-0002-1373-1705"/>
        <terms:date rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2020-07-30T12:00:00Z</terms:date>
        <oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>fly_anatomy.ontology</oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>
        <oboInOwl:hasRelatedSynonym>DNxn007</oboInOwl:hasRelatedSynonym>
        <oboInOwl:hasRelatedSynonym>PS069</oboInOwl:hasRelatedSynonym>
        <oboInOwl:id>FBbt:20001824</oboInOwl:id>
        <rdfs:comment>Cell type identified in multiple EM datasets (Scheffer et al., 2020; Schlegel et al., 2024; Dorkenwald et al., 2024; Marin et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025). Synapse locations are given where each cell of this type in neuprint has at least 10 connections.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>adult descending neuron of the anterior ventral brain DNbe005</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
