        <obo:IAO_0000115>Adult descending neuron of the posterior brain of the DNpe010 group (Berg et al., 2025). It belongs to the PSp3 hemilineage (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral gorget, vest, posterior lateral protocerebrum, inferior clamp, superior posterior slope, inferior posterior slope, wing neuropil and neck neuropil, the contralateral superior posterior slope, and the gnathal ganglion (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral gorget, superior posterior slope, inferior posterior slope, wing neuropil and neck neuropil, the contralateral superior posterior slope, and the gnathal ganglion (Berg et al., 2025). Its predicted neurotransmitter is glutamate (Eckstein et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <terms:contributor rdf:resource="http://orcid.org/0000-0002-1373-1705"/>
        <terms:date rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2020-07-30T12:00:00Z</terms:date>
