        <obo:IAO_0000115>Adult descending neuron of the outside anterior cluster of the DNde001 group (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral antennal lobe, vest, anterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, wedge, flange, T1 leg neuropil, T2 leg neuropil and T3 leg neuropil, the contralateral flange, and the ventral nerve cord, gnathal ganglion and saddle (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral accessory mesothoracic neuropil, vest, anterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, flange, T1 leg neuropil, T2 leg neuropil and T3 leg neuropil, the contralateral flange, T1 leg neuropil, T2 leg neuropil and T3 leg neuropil, and the gnathal ganglion and saddle (Berg et al., 2025). Its predicted neurotransmitter is glutamate (Eckstein et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <terms:contributor rdf:resource="http://orcid.org/0000-0002-1373-1705"/>
        <terms:date rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2020-07-30T12:00:00Z</terms:date>
