        <obo:IAO_0000115>Adult descending neuron of the posterior brain of the DNpe033 group (Berg et al., 2025). It belongs to the DM2 central hemilineage (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral superior medial protocerebrum and flange, and the gnathal ganglion, prow and intermediate tectulum (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral superior medial protocerebrum and flange, and the gnathal ganglion, prow and intermediate tectulum (Berg et al., 2025). Its predicted neurotransmitter is gaba (Eckstein et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <terms:contributor rdf:resource="http://orcid.org/0000-0002-1373-1705"/>
        <terms:date rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2020-07-30T12:00:00Z</terms:date>
