        <obo:IAO_0000115>Adult descending neuron of the outside anterior cluster of the DNde005 group (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral lateral accessory lobe, vest, inferior posterior slope, flange, T1 leg neuropil, T2 leg neuropil and T3 leg neuropil, and the cervical connective, gnathal ganglion, saddle and abdominal neuromere (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral vest, inferior posterior slope, flange, T1 leg neuropil, T2 leg neuropil and T3 leg neuropil, and the gnathal ganglion, saddle and abdominal neuromere (Berg et al., 2025). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025).</obo:IAO_0000115>
