            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Adult descending neuron of the posterior brain of the DNpe002 group (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral lateral accessory lobe, antennal mechanosensory and motor center, antennal lobe, gorget, epaulette, vest, posterior lateral protocerebrum, inferior clamp, wedge, superior posterior slope, flange, T1 leg neuropil, T2 leg neuropil and T3 leg neuropil, and the ventral nerve cord and gnathal ganglion (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral vest, T1 leg neuropil, T2 leg neuropil and T3 leg neuropil, and the ventral nerve cord and gnathal ganglion (Berg et al., 2025). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <terms:contributor rdf:resource="http://orcid.org/0000-0002-1373-1705"/>
        <terms:date rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2020-07-30T12:00:00Z</terms:date>
