        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Adult descending neuron of the posterior brain of the DNpe003 group (Berg et al., 2025). It receives input in the ipsilateral lateral accessory lobe, vest, posterior lateral protocerebrum, superior posterior slope, flange, T1 leg neuropil, T2 leg neuropil and T3 leg neuropil, and the ventral nerve cord, gnathal ganglion and saddle (Berg et al., 2025). It sends output to the ipsilateral haltere neuropil, T1 leg neuropil, T2 leg neuropil and T3 leg neuropil, and the gnathal ganglion and intermediate tectulum (Berg et al., 2025). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024; Berg et al., 2025).</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <terms:contributor rdf:resource="http://orcid.org/0000-0002-1373-1705"/>
        <terms:date rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2020-07-30T12:00:00Z</terms:date>
